      <figure class="image-float-left">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1622484212850-eb596d79cedb?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=600" alt="Slow copper-vat caramelization of Vietnamese cane juice into Tinh Hoa Mía" loading="lazy" />
        <figcaption>Copper vats seasoned over 40 years impart a subtle mineral complexity no modern equipment can replicate.</figcaption>
